description:
Equally at home around town, chopping wood, or hiking in the backcountry, this heavy-duty utility shirt offers easy-wearing comfort and rugged style. It can be worn by itself, as a lightweight jacket, or even a midlayer, thanks to the versatile pockets and buttoned sleeve plackets.Burly nylon with a bit of stretch stands up to camp life.PFC-free DWR finish sheds mist and mud.Durable double-stitch seams and double-layered reinforcements.Forward shoulder seams won't chafe under backpack straps.

        Sustainability






